law.history: Repealed 1964 Ky. Acts ch. 47, sec. 1, effective June 18, 1964. -- Created 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 185, secs. 1, 2, and 3, effective June 16, 1960.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Notice to voters before primary for state-wide officers of necessity of transferring registration record upon moving to another precinct.
